Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Brisbane are excited to present to the market for lease 13-15 Bowen Bridge Road, Bowen Hills. Situated in the heart of Bowen Hills, directly opposite the Royal Brisbane Hospital is a prime opportunity to secure a fully refurbished freestanding office/medical building in one of Brisbane's fastest growing precincts. 

-	449-966sqm high quality refurbished tenancies
-	Exceptional onsite car parking 
-	Brand new amenities
-	Full disability access
-	Abundance of natural light throughout 

Set over two levels, 13-15 Bowen Bridge Road, Bowen Hills has undergone a major building refurbishment. The building capital works program has included upgrading to LED lighting, stone tiled entrances, painting both internally and externally, ceilings, flooring, kitchens, bathrooms, building facades, gardens and car parking. The building has had a new roof installed, new ducted air-conditioning system throughout and a new Eletech Lift system. The building is currently open plan in layout. 

Public transport is at your doorstep with the RBH Bus Station directly opposite the building and Exhibition Station a 5 minute walk away. King Street is around the corner along with local coffee shops, cafes and restaurants. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: DIRECTLY OPPOSITE ROYAL BRISBANE HOSPITAL | FREESTANDING REFURBISHED BUILDING

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present to the market for lease 153 Campbell Street, Bowen Hills, more commonly recognised as ‘Citilink Business Centre’. The property comprises of approximately 15,669 sqm of quality office accommodation across two buildings, with over 275 onsite car parks. The owners have committed significant funds to replace the air-conditioning system and roof, upgrade lobby foyers and construct a new End of Trip facility. Much of this due to be completed in 2021.
   
  -  Tenancies from 189 to 1,200 sqm
  -  Refurbished and Spec Suite options available
  -  Excellent natural light throughout
  -  Brand new onsite cafe offering
  -  Suited to both office and medical use
  -  Onsite gym and tennis court 
  -  Excellent car parking ratio and visitor bays
  -  Fully PWD Compliant with disabled access
  -  3-star NABERS Energy Rating
  -  4.5-star NABER Water Rating
  -  6-star NABERS Energy Rating include Green power
  
153 Campbell Street, Bowen Hills is located directly opposite the Royal Brisbane Hospital and has easy access to Major Bus and Cycle interchange. The property has excellent access to major road infrastructure, including the Clem 7, Airport Link, Legacy Way Tunnels and major arterial roads. The property has a brand-new onsite cafe offering and is within minutes from the RNA Showgrounds re-development precinct, which offers a plethora of cafes, restaurants and award-winning bars.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents, CBRE.

CBRE are pleased to offer 9/7 O’Connell Terrace FOR LEASE, a prime corner position within the popular suburb of Bowen Hills.

An area of 129sqm, the building is being offered at a competitive rent.

The existing fit out includes:
• 1 Boardroom
• 5 good sized offices
• Meeting room
• Reception
• Kitchenette
• Internal toilets

The building offers outstanding exposure and prominent signage opportunity to busy O’Connell Terrace and Brookes Street.

This rare highly exposed opportunity is centrally located within the Bowen Hills precinct, directly opposite the RNA Showgrounds and King Street precinct which provides staff with an abundance of retail amenity. 

The property is extremely well serviced by all forms of public transport. Exhibition Station is located 150 metres from the property which provides direct passage further North, East or back into the CBD within minutes. Future Cross River Exhibition Station is located a walk away as well as a number of major bus stops featured along O’Connell Terrace and Brookes Streets. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the Exclusive CBRE Leasing Agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A rare opportunity is now available within 25 Montpelier Road, offering large efficient floors plates, excellent natural light, secure car parking and modern end-of-trip facilities. 

The property is easily accessible by all public transport and is strategically located in the Brisbane CBD - Brisbane Airport corridor. This precinct has seen unprecedented growth and popularity due to the diverse amenity currently available in the area for staff which includes The Homemaker and Emporium centres. These services are further amplified by the development of the Gasworks precinct, being 100 metres away. 

The current opportunity presents: 

• 500 - 755sqm office space, ready for occupation
• Fitout includes reception, boardrooms, ample meeting rooms & offices, open plan working areas and kitchen
• Excellent natural light throughout
• 15 car parks available at market rates 

For more information please contact CBRE.
